name: Smuggler's Blues
Lore: 'It''s the lure of easy credits. It''s got a very strong appeal. Perhaps you''d understand better wearing my flight suit. It''s the ultimate special modification, it''s the smuggler''s blues.',
Text: 'Deploy on a smuggler. May use 2 Force to cancel Limited Resources. Also, if ''trained'' by Rycar Ryjerd and piloting as starship when that starship completes Kessel Run, Rycar''s Run or The First Transport Is Away, any retrieved Force may be taken into hand.',
